POE:Component:Server:IRC
=====================================

This POE component is designed to provide an abstract, subclassable IRC
daemon framework. Internal structures are not concrete in design as of
this release. Please see the samples/ tree for code samples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

ExtUtils::MakeMaker
POE
Socket
Gtk (Optional)

